title: Square Invisible Cut Clear CZ Basket Set Sterling Silver Stud Earrings 7mm
description: Lots of sparkle are produced by a magnificent square kite basket checkerboard invisible cut diamond cz cubic zirconia stone in a 4-prong setting. These designer inspired stud earrings are made of solid .925 sterling silver. The earrings can be worn by men and women and for pierced ears only. You choose the cz carat weight: 4mm(0.40 ctw), 5mm (0.75ctw), 6mm (1ctw), 7mm (2ctw), 8mm (3 ctw) or 9mm (5 ctw).
